DBZ Abridged, by Team Four Star.

Here we have everything they posted prior to August 11, 2009 - The date they got kicked off a certain video hosting site due to Toei's complaints.

I've recreated the torrent on the basis that their second FAQ episode (added after the &quot;big wipe&quot;) has now also been deleted. So this new version includes that and a couple of short videos where they try to explain what's going on.

My connection's pretty slow, so remember to keep seeding for others when you're done!

